data.description: ***PRICE IMPROVEMENT***  Discover this perfect home for any growing family! As you step into the open foyer to your left is a multipurpose room that can be used for office, or game room. To the right you'll enjoy family gatherings in this spacious dining room and there is also a large family room, complete with a gas fireplace and entertainment center. The kitchen boasts white cabinets, stainless appliances, and a convenient butler's pantry. The owner's suite, three additional bedrooms, and a bonus room/5th bedroom over the garage offer built-ins and ample space for hobbies. Outside, a lovely screen porch for relaxing on warm summer evenings, a fenced yard, shed, and pond-fed irrigation system. Take advantage of neighborhood amenities andthe convenient location close to schools, parks, and more. The neighborhood has a pool, and play area, and a large field for picnics and outdoor activities. This is where the food trucks rally up every Thursday. There are multiple ponds that are stocked for fishing. Sidewalks all throughout the neighborhood that connects to the West Ashley walking trail. You can even walk or run the trail all the way to Hwy 17 if you want to.
